Collins Place (right), at the S.E. corner of 35th Avenue. This property was owned by Charlotte G. Prince in 1873 and 1891, but the old house does not appear on maps of the above years. It first appears on a 1909 atlas. View 2 shows the other side of the house.

P. L. Sperr

May 27, 1939
Views 1,2.
